cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.MA 

This paper is about benchmarking various model-based reinforcement learning algorithms, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The algorithms are tested on a variety of environments, including robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses challenges and future directions for model-based RL, which falls under the category of multi-agent systems (cs.MA).
